# ============================================================
# Parmetros
# ============================================================
1, 1 = 10.0, 1.0
2, 2 = 1.0, 0.5
x0 = [0.0, 1.0, 0.0, 1.0]
T = 1.564*3 # 4.0
Ncontrols = 3200 # 1200
Nsteps = 10 # 8

# ============================================================
# Dinmica del sistema (CORREGIDA)
# ============================================================
function spins!(dx, x, p, t)
    1, 1, 2, 2, u = p

    ut = u(t)   # <---- u evaluado en t (esto evita el error)

    dx[1] = -1 * x[1] - ut * x[2]
    dx[2] = 1 * (1 - x[2]) + ut * x[1]
    dx[3] = -2 * x[3] - ut * x[4]
    dx[4] = 2 * (1 - x[4]) + ut * x[3]
end

# ============================================================
# Control por tramos
# ============================================================
function make_u(tvec, uvals)
    function ufun(t)
        for i in 1:length(tvec)-1
            if tvec[i]  t < tvec[i+1]
                return uvals[i]
            end
        end
        return uvals[end]
    end
    return ufun
end

# ============================================================
# Barrido de controles
# ============================================================
ts = range(0, T, length = Nsteps + 1)
final_points = zeros(Float64, 4, Ncontrols)

Random.seed!(11)

for k in 1:Ncontrols

    uvals = rand(Nsteps) .* 2*1 .- 1*1        # valores en [-1,1] ## uvals = rand([-1.0, 1.0], Nsteps)
    u = make_u(ts, uvals)                 # funcin u(t)

    p = (1, 1, 2, 2, u)
    prob = ODEProblem(spins!, x0, (0.0, T), p)
    sol = solve(prob)

    final_points[:, k] = sol(T)
end

println("Acc(x0,T) aproximado con xito.")

# ============================================================
# Semicrculo superior (Bloch)
# ============================================================
 = range(0, 2, length=300)
yc = @. sin()
zc = @. cos()

# ============================================================
# Grficos
# ============================================================
p1 = scatter(final_points[1,:], final_points[2,:],
             xlabel="y", ylabel="z",
             title="Spin1_conjunto alcanzable:(y(T), z(T))",
             markersize=3, legend=false,

             titlefontsize=28,

# Parmetros
1, 1 = 3.0, 1.0
2, 2 = 1.0, 0.5 

u = -1.0 # u constante con |u|<=1

# Sistema de EDO
function spins!(dx, x, p, t)
    1, 1, 2, 2, u = p

    dx[1] = -1 * x[1] - u * x[2]          # 
    dx[2] = 1 * (1 - x[2]) + u * x[1]     # 
    dx[3] = -2 * x[3] - u * x[4]          # 
    dx[4] = 2 * (1 - x[4]) + u * x[3]     # 
end

# Condicin inicial
x0 = [0.0, 1.0, 0.0, 1.0]

# Intervalo de tiempo
T = 50.0
tspan = (0.0, T)

# Paquete de parmetros
p = (1, 1, 2, 2, u)

# Definir problema
prob = ODEProblem(spins!, x0, tspan, p)

# Resolver
sol = solve(prob)

# --------- Nuevo: contraste |q1 - q2| ---------
q1 = sqrt.(sol[1,:].^2 .+ sol[2,:].^2)
q2 = sqrt.(sol[3,:].^2 .+ sol[4,:].^2)
contraste = abs.(q1 .- q2)

# --------- Grfico principal ---------
p1 = plot(sol,
          xlabel = "t",
          ylabel = "x(t)",
          label = ["y(t)" "z(t)" "y(t)" "z(t)"],
          lw = 2,
          title = "Dinmica de dos spins con u = -1.0")

# --------- Grfico del contraste ---------
p2 = plot(sol.t, contraste,
          lw = 3,
          xlabel = "t",
          ylabel = "|q - q|",
          label = "c(t)",
          title = "Contraste entre los dos spins")

plot(p1, p2, layout = (2,1))

# Parmetros del modelo
 = 5
T_min = 2.437
#
T =  * T_min # tiempo final fijo con >=1
1, 1 = 1.2, 0.5
2, 2 = 1.0, 0.5 

# Definicin del problema de control ptimo
ocp = @def begin
    t  [0, T], time
    x  R, state   # x = [y1, z1, y2, z2]
    u  R, control

    # Condiciones iniciales
    x(0) == [0.0, 1.0, 0.0, 1.0]
    
    # Condiciones finales para el spin 1 (saturacin)
    x(T)[1] == 0.0
    x(T)[2] == 0.0

    # Dinmica del sistema (dos spins)
    x(t) == [
        -1 * x[1](t) - u(t) * x[2](t),                      # 
         1 * (1 - x[2](t)) + u(t) * x[1](t),                # 
        -2 * x[3](t) - u(t) * x[4](t),                      # 
         2 * (1 - x[4](t)) + u(t) * x[3](t)                 # 
    ]

    # Restriccin de control
    -1  u(t)  1
    # 
    x[1](t)^2 + x[2](t)^2  1
    x[3](t)^2 + x[4](t)^2  1

    # Funcin objetivo: maximizar (y_2 + z_2)   minimizar -(y_2 + z_2)
    # Obs: ( 1 * u(t)^2 ) - 0.5 * (x(T)[3]^2 + x(T)[4]^2)  min
    -1.0 * (x(T)[3]^2 + x(T)[4]^2)  min
end

sol = solve(ocp; display=false)
#sol = solve(ocp; grid_size=250, display=false)
#sol = solve(ocp)

#plot(sol) 
plot(sol, :state,:control,:costate;                 
     costate_style = (color=:black,), 
     control_style = (color=:red, linewidth=2),
     control_bounds_style = (linestyle = :dash,))

function Problema(,T_min,1,1,2,2)
    T =  * T_min  # tiempo final

    # Definicin del problema de control ptimo
    ocp = @def begin
        t  [0, T], time
        x  R, state   # x = [y1, z1, y2, z2]
        u  R, control

        # Condiciones iniciales
        x(0) == [0.0, 1.0, 0.0, 1.0]

        # Condiciones finales para el spin 1 (saturacin)
        x(T)[1] == 0.0
        x(T)[2] == 0.0

        # Dinmica del sistema (dos spins)
        x(t) == [
            -1 * x[1](t) - u(t) * x[2](t),                      # 
             1 * (1 - x[2](t)) + u(t) * x[1](t),                # 
            -2 * x[3](t) - u(t) * x[4](t),                      # 
             2 * (1 - x[4](t)) + u(t) * x[3](t)                 # 
        ]

        # Restriccin de control
        -1  u(t)  1
        # 
        x[1](t)^2 + x[2](t)^2  1
        x[3](t)^2 + x[4](t)^2  1

        # Funcin objetivo
        -1.0 * (x(T)[3]^2 + x(T)[4]^2)  min
    end

    # Resolver el problema
    sol = solve(ocp; display=false)
    
    xT = sol.state.value(T)
    println("y(T) = ", round(xT[1], digits=3))
    println("z(T) = ", round(xT[2], digits=3))
    println("Valor de la funcin objetivo = ", sol.objective,"\n")
    
    println("""
    ================ Parmetros del grfico ================
          = $
    T_min  = $T_min
    T      = $( * T_min)
    1     = $1
    1     = $1
    2     = $2
    2     = $2
    ========================================================
    """)
    
    #p1 = plot(sol, :control;                  
    #     costate_style = (color=:black,), 
    #     control_style = (color=:red, linewidth=2),
    #     control_bounds_style = (linestyle = :dash,))
    
    # --- Construir el tiempo ---
    Time = range(0,  * T_min, length=501)

    # --- Extraer estados y coestados ---
    x_control = [sol.control.value(t) for t in Time]
    #
    x = [sol.state.value(t) for t in Time]   # Cada x[t] es un vector [x1,x2,x3,x4]
    p = [sol.costate(t) for t in Time]       # Cada p[t] es un vector [p1,p2,p3,p4]

    # --- Construir la seal  f(t) = -p1*x2 + p2*x1 - p3*x4 + p4*x3 ---
    f = [
        -p[t][1] * x[t][2] +
         p[t][2] * x[t][1] -
         p[t][3] * x[t][4] +
         p[t][4] * x[t][3]
        for t in 1:length(Time)
    ]
    
    # --- Graficar ---
    p1 = plot(Time, x_control,
        xlabel = "t",
        ylabel = "u*(t)",         # smbolo en cursiva
        title  = "Control",
        lw = 2,
        color = :red,
        legend = false,
        titlefontsize = 28,
        guidefontsize = 27,
        tickfontsize = 14
        )

    # --- Graficar phi(t) ---
    p = plot(Time, -f,
        xlabel = "t",
        ylabel = "(t)",         # smbolo en cursiva
        title  = "Funcin de Conmutacin",
        lw = 2,
        legend = false,
        titlefontsize = 28,
        guidefontsize = 27,
        tickfontsize = 14
        )
    
    t=0.0
    for i in 1:length(Time)
        if Time[i] > 10 && f[i] >= 0
            t = Time[i]
            break  # Opcional: si solo quieres el primer valor que cumple la condicin
        end
    end
        
    vline!(p, [8], color=:green, linestyle=:dot, lw=2)
    vline!(p, [t], color=:green, linestyle=:dot, lw=2)
    plot(p1, p, layout=(2,1), size=(1400,1200), margin=10mm, top_margin=15mm)
end
